                                  @{fg shine}History@{fg text}
        _______________________________________________________________
        
        @{b}1 Aug. 95:@{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.0@{uu}
                   Initial working version.
                   
        @{b}2 Aug. 95:@{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.1@{uu}
                   A view problems in the code when stripping the markups.
                   &'s were added thanx to Robert "sprit" Anderson.
                   
        @{b}3 Aug. 95:@{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.2@{uu}
                   Decided to add localization to the program.
        
        @{b}5 Aug. 95:@{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.3@{uu}
                   BETTA RELEASE
       @{b}19 Feb. 96:@{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.4@{uu}
                   %%%%%
                   %%%%% Fixed? A parsing problem that crashed the
                   %%%%% system
                   %%%%%
       @{b}5 May. 96:@{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.5@{uu}
                   Even faster conversions!!!
       @{b}15 May. 96:@{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.6@{uu}
                   ADDED .htm to the search
       @{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.7@{uu}
                   Not released publicly.
       @{b}30 Oct. 96:@{ub} @{u}HTML-TEXT v1.8@{uu}
                   This is the full version.
                   Changed the 'CONVERT' gad to disabled
                   untill the there were files to be converted,
                   this is mostly asthetic :)
                   Tweaked the conversion routine.
                   Added an Install script.
@endnode

